description: A deep-sea diver stands on the ocean floor, his air hose tied in multiple complex knots above him. Bubbles rise from his helmet as he looks up towards the underside of the boat on the surface. This absurd scenario creates dark humor, highlighting the potential consequences of incompetence in a life-threatening environment. The tangled hose renders the vital air supply useless in a surreal display of misfortune.
